videos.description: Jarvis Omersa ends up on the other side of a Marcus Carr alley-oop, after Minnesota wins an intense battle for the rebound on the defensive end.
videos.headline: Omersa, Carr connect after intense battle on the defensive end for Minnesota

videos.description: Darryl Morsell shoots the J from way back and nails the deep 3-pointer to give Maryland the 74-73 win over Minnesota.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Morsell's deep 3 wins it for No. 9 Maryland) 2020/02/26 ESHEETS

videos.headline: Morsell's deep 3 wins it for No. 9 Maryland
